channel.title: Elysium OSRS - IRONMAN - HIGHSCORES
channel.description:
Hello everyone! :cool: :D
Here to show you a brand new server called Elysium, i could go ahead and explain it to you, but why not just join us and give it a try yourself? Like Flame said, dont judge a book by its cover.
Here we have some features! ;) Many more to come, we are updating daily!
-IRONMAN mode [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/5147224/ironman.png[/img]
- Dicing
- Duel arena
-Boss pets
-Elite slayer tasks
-+ alot more
ACHIEVEMENTS! [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/5127542/archievements.png[/img]
Clue Scrolls just like the old days! [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/5127546/clue_scrolls.png[/img] BOSSES
- Chaos Elemental
-Godwars
-Barrelchest
-KBD
-Dagannoth Kings
-Kraken
-Mithril dragons [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/5148087/bosslogs.png[/img]
-Callisto
-Venenatis
-Vet'ion
-Scorpia
-Giant sea snake [img]http://s13.postimg.org/7xhjnr3qf/wildy_bosses.png[/img]
MINIGAMES
-Barrows
- Pest Control
- Jad Mini-game
- Duel arena
- Warriors Guild
- Barbarian Assault
Here is what you need to start being a member of our community! [url=http://elysiumps.com/]Website[/url] [url=https://www.dropbox.com/s/vf0n60uzi8158up/elysium.jar?dl=1]Desktop Client[/url]
